Package: WindSuitabilityNRW
Type: Package
Title: Wind Energy Suitability Analysis for North Rhine-Westphalia
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
  "Samuel", "Yohanna",
  email = "samuel.yohanna@uni-muenster.de",
  role  = c("aut", "cre")
  )
Description: Provides spatial analysis tools for evaluating wind energy
  development potential in North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany. Implements
  German planning regulations and environmental constraints to identify
  suitable areas for wind turbine installation.
